metadata.name: Golden Mutant Monkey
metadata.description:
Golden Mutant Monkey Robot

The legend of the Golden Mutant Monkey is a tale of a small troop of Golden Monkeys who lived peacefully deep in the jungle until toxic waste dumped by the greedy corporation caused a horrible rash of mutations.

Now under the dark of night the tribe of Golden Mutant Monkeys avenge corporate greed, only rare glimpses of them are ever reported, captured in this unique collection of NFTâ€™s is artists renditions of witness accounts!
